The paper deals with image reconstruction using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of a convolutional neural network (CNN) also suggests that the paper may fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category. The iterative nature of the method and the use of a linear reconstruction operator may also suggest that the paper could be categorized under information theory (cs.IT) or numerical analysis (cs.NA).
